{"data":[{"id":563956362,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d3604c47855458be43f79261b33d14c0","url_token":"lycheer-26","name":"lycheer","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d60f33c7396af34bc444ddc094a03d20_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d60f33c7396af34bc444ddc094a03d20_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d3604c47855458be43f79261b33d14c0","user_type":"people","headline":"目标是 做一个金刚芭比","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563956362","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546315067,"updated_time":1546315067,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":2,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"怎么说，我更确信这是一场营销。这个高中生身上存在太多疑点，甚至我怀疑他根本不是高中生。\u003cbr\u003e①他常用错别字。在发表的文章中，“望见谅”写成“忘见谅”，还有一些别的错别字，但是现在文章被他删了，我无法截图。更让人不可思议的是，在他手写的证明过程中，“哥德巴赫猜想”被写成了“歌德巴赫猜想”。当然，有知友说这只是音译问题，无伤大雅。但是他本人再次发表文章，说他的确写错字。\u003cbr\u003e我真的很想问一句，一个高中生，接受了九年义务教育的学生，真的会出现如此高频率的错别字现象吗？\u003cbr\u003e②他装疯卖傻。信誓旦旦地说自己证明了哥猜，于是到知乎来提问，并且扬言要在知乎公布。又吊足大家胃口说1月1日公布证明过程，期间还发表了“如果我届时无法提供证明过程，会怎么样？”的言论，他彻底地秉持着一种调戏的姿态。证明发布出来后，被迅速打脸，半夜删掉自己的证明过程，宣称自己要销号。白天仍然发动态，并且再次发表文章企图证明“我想销号啊，但是知乎不理我，不是我的错”。他作为一个高中生究竟是不会查百度，还是装疯卖傻，大家可以自行定夺。\u003cbr\u003e③他删我评论。在今天早上他发表的文章当中，他说要把自己的证明过程存档起来，以免知友看不见。我是第二个评论的人，我评论的内容如下：销号就销号，不要搞那么多五五六六七七八八的。吃完中午饭回来，我的评论就不见了。为什么要删除我的评论？这个回答就是从你删评这个举动引发的，如果你真的打算销号，你就该拿出你应有的态度和行为，而不是拿出扭扭捏捏的姿态。你可是还在文章里说自己是“河北男人”的，你可记得吗？\u003cbr\u003e④有一个回答说，他的确不是高中生，他已经是一个将近三十岁的“大孩子”了。我不能确定那个回答的真假，当然，那个答主说自己的回答是真的。其实无论他的身份是高中生还是一个三十岁的男人，他的所作所为都让人很无奈。有这个想法与勇气固然是好，但是你如果把它当作是卖弄自己的资本，其实就是对知识的藐视。\u003cbr\u003e最后，取消关注的操作，是必不可少的。","editable_content":"","excerpt":"怎么说，我更确信这是一场营销。这个高中生身上存在太多疑点，甚至我怀疑他根本不是高中生。 ①他常用错别字。在发表的文章中，“望见谅”写成“忘见谅”，还有一些别的错别字，但是现在文章被他删了，我无法截图。更让人不可思议的是，在他手写的证明过程…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=479\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_i